floods and provide water for irrigation.<ref>{{cite web|title=A Feasibility Study and Design of the Bawanur Dam and Irrigation System, Iraq 2010 - 2012|url=http://www.creacz.com/en/Aktivita3/|publisher=CREA|accessdate=20 April 2016}}</ref> In August 2013, the [[Kurdistan Regional Government]] signed a US$200 million contract with the Romanian firm, [[Hidroconstrucția]], to build the dam and power station. The project is expected to be complete in 2018.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kurdistan Signs $200 Million Contract With Romanian Firm for Dam Construction|url=https://www.ooskanews.com/story/2013/08/kurdistan-signs-200-million-contract-romanian-firm-dam-construction_157110|publisher=Ooska News|accessdate=20 April 2016|date=8 August 2013}}</ref>
