'''PNNM''' is a similar explosive to [[ANFO#ANNM|ANNM]], it consists of [[potassium nitrate]] and [[nitromethane]] in the ratio of 60:40 w/w respectively.  It can be [[Detonation|detonated]] with a grade 8 cap and often has [[aluminium]] powder added.

